answers.body_markdown:
You have forgotten to tell your nodes that, they belong to a replica set!
You have two choices, command line:

    mongod --replSet &quot;rs0&quot; --bind_ip localhost,&lt;hostname(s)|ip address(es)&gt;

or inside of config -file

    replication:
       replSetName: &quot;rs0&quot;
    net:
       bindIp: localhost,&lt;hostname(s)|ip address(es)&gt;

Check more information from [here!][1]


  [1]: https://docs.mongodb.com/manual/tutorial/deploy-replica-set/

